    "From the dataset, eighty scans were used for training all three models, and ten were used for evaluation.",
    "One-hundred simulated X-ray images were generated for each CT scan using DiffDRR.",
    "15 The source-to-detector distance was set to 1020 mm, and the image size 768 × 768.",
    "All images are then rescaled to 512 × 512 prior to training.",
    "Data and Experimental SettingRandom rotations (r x, r y, r z) within the range of [-45, 45] degrees and random translations (t x, t y, t z) within the range of [-50, 50] were applied for image and landmark projection using DiffDRR."
